{"tid":837043,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Hebe、Selina也掰了華研！S.H.E 4億金雞母全飛走","createTime":"2018-09-26T05:38:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T12:11:02.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f95545cd1cff871f44f63ff6dc9fc9e603c19c81","tid":837043,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:38:11.000Z","msg":"台灣女子天團S.H.E驚傳要分崩離析！今年7月先傳出Ella將離開待了17年的華研，10月起將經紀約收回並由老公賴斯翔打理。不料，今再傳Selina和Hebe在9月底約滿後通通要離開華研，不再續約，各自分飛。<br />\n<br />\n華研晚間發聲明間「S.H.E三位成員與本公司合作尚未屆期， 接下來三人將各自成立個人公司，未來期間合作內容仍在討論中，其他相關資訊請看證券櫃台買賣中心公開資訊觀測站， 以公告為準」。 <br />\n<br />\n賴斯翔辭去原本的工作，以Ella專屬顧問在華研國際為Ella把關工作，而他已註冊成立「勁樺娛樂有限公司」，也是未來為Ella量身打造的公司。<br />\n<br />\n3姝都將離開，對華研打擊頗大，去年Selina有7支代言，估計收入6000萬元台幣；Hebe更是最大「搖錢樹」，去年11支代言，光廣告酬勞破億。粗估3姝去年共為華研賺進逾4億元台幣。<br />\n<br />\n不過，因「S.H.E」的團名是屬於華研，當初傳單飛不解散，3人都說彼此已是一家人，還是有合體的可能。但未來要再合體，仍須經過有團名版權的華研統整辦理。<br />\n<br />\n華研音樂近期受到藝人出走影響，股價表現偏弱，今日盤中最低價跌至每股98.1元，創21個月來新低；若以華研股本5.44億元估計，華研市值由逾65億元降至約53億元，市值蒸發逾11億元。（張哲鳴／台北報導）出版時間：15：16<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180925/1435986/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180925%2F1435986%2F&d=GLlPsK05qGU%2FIJO3gfn48pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=9aacec99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180925%2F1435986%2F&h=80a763e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180925/1435986/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d57a30725a6273860efee8817f2f9104c396e00","tid":837043,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:06:42.000Z","msg":"放過e啦"},{"pid":"74e9312f0159760383c24d9ccfa42dc32ab892df","tid":837043,"uid":89931,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T12:43:56.000Z","msg":"抵啦垃圾公司乜嘢都唔做"},{"pid":"33fbddecc06250b8063667a743bc920de0998c7f","tid":837043,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"74e9312f0159760383c24d9ccfa42dc32ab892df","tid":837043,"uid":89931,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T12:43:56.000Z","msg":"抵啦垃圾公司乜嘢都唔做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T12:45:45.000Z","msg":"好似勁撚耐先出碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510e5c62b6b2a770b07cc870bba74f6959773747","tid":837043,"uid":171594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T12:49:42.000Z","msg":"唔知走晒出黎仲會唔會再合體出碟"},{"pid":"e95f77d48852c0002db5a159990ccfbc416dff9f","tid":837043,"uid":4917,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:00:00.000Z","msg":"華研都唔識捧人嘅，除左she無個得咁滯<br />\n而家連she D歌都越嚟越差，淨係可以賣集體回憶"},{"pid":"c80c3841cac237f64139064f4eb3bd04f5925001","tid":837043,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e95f77d48852c0002db5a159990ccfbc416dff9f","tid":837043,"uid":4917,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:00:00.000Z","msg":"華研都唔識捧人嘅，除左she無個得咁滯<br />\n而家連she D歌都越嚟越差，淨係可以賣集體回憶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:14:49.000Z","msg":"我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHebe出去唱仲loop緊頭一兩隻碟啲歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad6e371dc71ab26b34e82a145e9107cd1f7c270","tid":837043,"uid":196855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e95f77d48852c0002db5a159990ccfbc416dff9f","tid":837043,"uid":4917,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:00:00.000Z","msg":"華研都唔識捧人嘅，除左she無個得咁滯<br />\n而家連she D歌都越嚟越差，淨係可以賣集體回憶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T04:02:35.000Z","msg":"其實loop